author: Anonymous Scale
title: 2019w2-f Question5 Does the arrangement matter?
question:
I get the same answer as the solution but the answers' arrangements are different. Does that matter for getting full marks?
 Actual value
(list
 (make-count "A" 1)
 (make-count "C" 2)
 (make-count "D" 2)
 (make-count "B" 2)
 (make-count "E" 3))
differs from
(list
 (make-count "D" 2)
 (make-count "C" 2)
 (make-count "A" 1)
 (make-count "E" 3)
 (make-count "B" 2))
the expected value.
